                p Matthew Joyce Tyson, Geraldine DeForde, Ella Semorskaya, Daniel DeMartini, and Daniel Morse, with permission from University of California Santa Barbara.
              .well
                h4 Usage Restrictions
                p Please cite the owner of the video when publishing. This video may be freely used by reporters as part of news coverage, with proper attribution. Non-reporters must contact <em>Science</em> for permission.

